# Claude Code: share agents + team settings, keep local overrides and cache
# out of git. Our convention:
#   .claude/agents/*.md        — team-shared (committed)
#   .claude/settings.json      — team-shared, if present (committed)
#   .claude/settings.local.json — per-developer overrides (ignored)
#   .claude/agent-memory/      — local cache (ignored)
